Medical Corp unit to Angola. Later this week Deputy Minister 
Beilin will meet UN Secretary General Butrus-Ghali for 
discussing the location to which the IDF's [Israel Defense 
Forces] representatives are to be sent. The place will be one of 
the conflict ridden areas in Africa. Our correspondent notes 
that Israel prefers to send soldiers to areas in which it has 
strategic interests, such as the Horn of Africa. 

