<F P=104>  Beirut AL-'AHD </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Report entitled "Beware of the U.S. Ambassador"] </F>
  [Text] U.S. Ambassador Mark Hambley has been holding weekly 
meetings with Lebanese journalists at the U.S. Embassy in 
'Awkar. At these meetings, Hambley leaks false reports to the 
journalists on U.S. policy in Lebanon and the region so that 
these reports will be published in the Lebanese press and lead 
to confusion in the Lebanese political club [al-nadi al-siyasi 
al-lubnani], which is at a "crossroads" with the new ambassador. 

