Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1602193894 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Voice of Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Foreign Minister Fariz Buwayz had denied that U.S. 
Secretary of State Warren Christopher's message has included any 
Israeli threats. 
  He told REUTER that the escalation of violence in the south 
is the result of the Israeli occupation. He said that achieving 
quick progress in the peace talks toward recognition of the 
principle of withdrawal from the south is needed to calm the 
situation. 

</TEXT>

