Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Israel today released three fishermen detained near 
Tyre. The Israeli Navy yesterday arrested five Lebanese 
fishermen aboard three boats. Israel released two of the five 
yesterday and released the other three today after interrogating 
them, according to Lebanese security sources. 

