<F P=100> LEBANON </F>
<H3> <TI>   Palestinians Admit Role </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC1602172594 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1630 GMT 16 Feb 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1602172594 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The two Palestinian defendants Salim Qasim Mihyu and 
Yusuf Sha'ban have confessed to the crime of killing Jordanian 
diplomat Na'ib al-Ma'atiyah. 
  Beirut's First Investigation Judge Sa'id Mirza today 
concluded his investigations by interrogating defendants Bassam 
'Abdallah Muhammad 'Atiyah and 'Afaf Yusuf. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

