today to Russian Federation President Boris Yeltsin. Foreign 
Minister Faruq al-Shar' handed the message to Russian Ambassador 
in Damascus Aleksandr Zotov. 
  The message is in reply to a message President Yeltsin sent 
to President Hafiz al-Asad on 8 January. 

