<F P=102>  NC1702163794 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Islamic Revolution 
in Arabic 1430 GMT 17 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1702163794 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Islamic Revolution 
in Arabic 1430 GMT 17 Feb 94 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Informed sources have affirmed that they have seen 
the tyrant Saddam's forces massing 3 km from the border strip 
with Kuwait in the area between Umm Qasr and (Hafr al-Batin). 
Our sources in al-Basrah quote these sources as saying that 
Saddam's authorities are currently sending reinforcements to 
their forces there consisting of armored units and advanced 
tanks, which are being moved at night from various main points 
in the al-Basrah, al-Nasiriyah, and al-'Amarah Governorates. 
  The sources said the troops massing on the border with 
Kuwait 
are among the elite units of the Presidential Guard, which 
underwent many courses and combat training recently. 

