  [Text] Leader President Saddam Husayn has received a 
thank-you cable from Fidel Castro, president of Cuba's Council 
of State and Council of Ministers, in reply to the two cables of 
congratulations his excellency sent on the Cuban Revolution 
Anniversary and the New Year. 
