<H3> <TI>   Pakistan Warned Not To Submit Resolution to UN Commission </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK1702154794 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1430 
GMT 17 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1702154794 </F>
