  [Text] The overall situation in Lebanon was the subject of 
Prime Minister Rafiq al-Hariri's talks with Syrian President 
Hafiz al-Asad yesterday. The NATIONAL NEWS AGENCY reports that 
President al-Asad met with Prime Minister al-Hariri for three 
