Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Foreign Minister Husayn Sulayman Abu-Salih has 
expressed regret that the Sudanese opposition is seeking 
protection from foreign forces to achieve its goals. He said 
the foremost concern of the so-called opposition is now an 
attempt to impose sanctions against Sudan. He added that the 
meeting in the British House of Commons in which the scattered 
