He said the opposition's talk of a war of extermination taking 
place in the south is completely devoid of truth and that Sudan 
denies the prejudiced allegations against it. He said what is 
going in the south at present is fighting between the various 
factions of the rebellion and that the Sudanese Army is doing 
its duty to spread security and to preserve the unity of Sudan. 

